</item>
<item>
 <title>SDS Information Checklist</title>
 <link>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/resources/sds-information-checklist</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-who field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Who is it for?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The SDS Information Checklist is for anyone giving information about self-directed support. &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;What does it do?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The SDS Information Checklist is designed to achieve quality and consistency in the local delivery of SDS information. It lists 4 key areas that information providers  should know about SDS before signposting people to relevant information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-how field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;How can you use it?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The SDS Information Checklist could be given to information providers and used when they are talking to individuals. It could also be used in team training and inductions. The checklist contains information specific to East Renfrewshire but can be adapted for use in other areas of Scotland.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
 <pubDate>Wed, 07 Jan 2015 15:36:19 +0000</pubDate>
 <dc:creator>Kate Dowling</dc:creator>
 <guid isPermaLink="false">165 at https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk</guid>
 <comments>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/resources/sds-information-checklist#comments</comments>
</item>
<item>
 <title>SDS Mapping Tool</title>
 <link>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/resources/sds-mapping-tool</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-who field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Who is it for?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The SDS Mapping Tool is for anyone supporting a person through their SDS journey.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;What does it do?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The SDS Mapping Tool maps all the people and steps involved in an individual’s journey to SDS. It is designed to help the person know who is involved, what their roles are, what each step will be and when it will take place so that they can exercise as much choice and control as possible over the process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-how field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;How can you use it?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The SDS Mapping Tool is designed to be hung on a wall as a calendar. The key or main supporter should take the lead in supporting the person to request photographs and contact details for each person and recording each step (meetings, telephone calls etc.) as they are arranged.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
 <pubDate>Wed, 07 Jan 2015 14:36:19 +0000</pubDate>
 <dc:creator>admin_pilotlight</dc:creator>
 <guid isPermaLink="false">95 at https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk</guid>
 <comments>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/resources/sds-mapping-tool#comments</comments>
</item>
<item>
 <title>Hints and Tips for setting up a Facebook Group</title>
 <link>https://pilotlight.iriss.org.uk/resources/hints-and-tips-setting-facebook-group</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-who field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Who is it for?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The hints and tips are for anyone (or group of people) looking to set up an open, closed or secret Facebook group.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;What does it do?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot; property=&quot;content:encoded&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;The hints and tips should help people understand the differences between open, closed and secret Facebook groups, advice about being a group administrator, moderating comments and tagging.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-resource-how field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;How can you use it?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;The hints are tips are available to download and keep.&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
